<p>Way too much crossword glue. These days, a puzzle can&#39;t allow TENN ERN RIATA SDAK UKE ATRI anymore, unless it was all working for an incredible theme. What ADRAG, indeed.</p>

<p>Yes, it&#39;s tough to execute on six themers, all of them pretty long. But there are a lot of ways of executing on six themers that work much better.</p>

